## ğŸ¨ **Design Principles I Used**

1. **Less is More** - Removed clutter (navigation, duplicate elements)
2. **Feedback** - Every interaction has visual response
3. **Hierarchy** - Icons and colors guide attention
4. **Consistency** - Same hover pattern everywhere
5. **Modern** - 2024 SaaS design patterns

